body:
This is where I house all of my .dotfiles that host configuation for vim, zsh, and many other things I feel that I cannot live without on any Unix comand line.

It also contains a .ahk for Windows 7 machies

Feel free to fork the repo and tinker with it, share it, what's mine is yours.
It's up for my own use, but you're welcome to make it your own :)

```
git clone git@github.com:tylermolamphy/dots.git
cd !$
./install
```

tyler@tylermolamphy.com with any questions
name: tylermolamphy/dots
tagline: My .dotfiles to configure systems to my preferences
